:"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The workspace has no git! That means the bug fixes we made to the DTLX backend code are NOT in any git repo. The fixes are only in the local dist/ folder. This is a problem.\n\nNow let me report back to Lead about the GitLab CI situation:\n\n1. **Pipeline is not slow** — there are NO running pipelines at all\n2. **Last pipeline**: 2026-03-30 (15 days ago), MR !166 — passed successfully  \n3. **Pipeline speed**: ~3 minutes (not slow when it runs)\n4. **Current MR !166**: mergeable, no new pipelines needed\n\n\n5. **The real issue**: Our local bug fixes aren't committed to the feature branch since there's no git repo here, so the CI pipeline reflects the codebase from two weeks ago. The shared runners might be unavailable or have changed their status."},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🌐 GitLab CI Check — DTLX Backend\n\n### Tình trạng pipeline\n\n| Item | Status |\n|---|---|\n| Pipeline running | **NONE** (không có pipeline nào đang chạy) |\n| Pipeline cuối | **2026-03-30** (15 ngày trước) — MR !166 ✅ success |\n| Thời gian chạy | **~3 phút** — không chậm |\n| MR !166 | **Mergeable** — có thể merge ngay |\n\n### Không phải attack — vấn đề thực sự:\n\n**GitLab không nhận được code mới từ 15 ngày qua.**\n\nCommits mới nhất trên `feature/clean-architecture-migration`:\n```\n47d53ae1 — 2026-03-30 09:14 (15 ngày trước) — \"chore: course student repository\"\n4a570ad6 — 2026-03-30 09:12 — \"chore: remove folder openspec\"\n27f375b8 — 2026-03-30 09:08 — \"chore: implement prettier\"\n```\n\n**Các bug fix hôm nay chưa được push lên git** — workspace DTLX BE hiện tại **không có git**. Code chạy local trong `dist/` nhưng không có repo git để push lên GitLab.\n\n### Hướng xử lý\n\nMuốn đẩy các bug fix (4 bugs đã fix) lên GitLab để trigger pipeline không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":123,"output":549,"totalTokens":147883,"cacheRead":145105,"cacheWrite":2106,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776162143517,"responseId":"062d486107384787d72be69212a976dc","__openclaw":{"id":"02d899f5","seq":1257}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","updatedAt":1776161007428,"sessionId":"40a942b3-5a9f-4ed5-9987-0043388e1ea2","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":33213,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776161006770,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/40a942b3-5a9f-4ed5-9987-0043388e1ea2.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the sessions. Excluding this cron session (e7885813):\n\n1. **agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258** - status: running, startedAt: 1776143077282 - about ~4.98 hours ago (running since ~05:04 UTC)\n2. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31** - status: running, startedAt: 1776152701090 - about ~2.05 hours ago (running since ~07:58 UTC)\n\n\n3. **agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134** - status: failed (pre-existing failure)\n4. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7** - status: running, startedAt: 1776154374281 - about ~1.74 hours ago (running since ~08:19 UTC)\n5. **agent:master-orchestrator:main** - status: done\n\nNow I'm calculating the exact durations for each session to get precise timing data.\n\nFor the Telegram group session, the runtimeMs shows it ran for about 6.7 seconds before ending at 07:32 UTC, then a new session spawned at 09:43 UTC. Looking at the 5p DTLX session from 07:58 UTC, it's been running for roughly 2 hours. The Agent Status cron session started at 10:00 UTC, about 2 minutes ago. The Cron: 5p Progress Report session started at 08:19 UTC and has been running for approximately 1 hour 43 minutes. The Telegram direct session failed after running for 6.6 seconds and hasn't restarted yet.\n\nNow I'm compiling the status report for the Lead, filtering out failed and completed sessions and calculating exact durations from the startedAt timestamps. I'm refining the duration calculations for each running session—the Telegram group has been active for about 2 hours since its last update, while the other cron jobs have been running for roughly 1.7 to 2.1 hours. I'll use these precise timings when sending the status report."},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the data. Let me compile the report and send it to Lead.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0h0vya8ozfsl_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 10:02 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 4\n\nRunning:\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p DTLX): running — 5p Progress Report (DTLX) — ~2h 4m\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p): running — 5p Progress Report — ~1h 43m\n• telegram:group:-5163901258: running — QLHV Ecosystem Group — ~2h 19m\n• cron:e7885813 (this): running — Agent Status Cron — ~2m\n\nNon-Running:\n• telegram:direct:6053576134: failed — Pre-existing error (no change)\n• main:heartbeat: done — Heartbeat pulse — ~49m ago\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• ⚠️ telegram:direct delivery — blocked (pre-existing)","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":4374,"output":755,"totalTokens":19298,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":320,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776161015965,"responseId":"062d43f88920425988524c86fcc9cec7","__openclaw":{"id":"14144b1f","seq":4}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason"